# Stack Constraints

## Frontend — ALLOWED
- Next.js (App Router) — routing, SSR
- shadcn/ui — all UI components (Button, Card, Input, Badge, Select, Toast, etc.)
- Tailwind CSS — all styling
- TanStack Query (`@tanstack/react-query`) — ALL server state, data fetching, caching
- React Hook Form + Zod — ALL forms and validation
- Axios — HTTP client (already configured in `src/lib/api.ts`)
- lucide-react — icons

## Frontend — FORBIDDEN
- ❌ Redux, Zustand, Jotai, Recoil — no client state libs for server data
- ❌ SWR, Apollo — use TanStack Query
- ❌ Formik, react-final-form — use React Hook Form
- ❌ MUI, Ant Design, Chakra — use shadcn/ui
- ❌ styled-components, emotion — use Tailwind CSS
- ❌ Plain CSS modules for layout — use Tailwind

## Backend — ALLOWED
- NestJS — framework
- Prisma — database ORM
- nestjs-pino — structured JSON logging
- prom-client — Prometheus metrics
- @sentry/nestjs — error tracking
- class-validator + class-transformer — DTO validation
- @nestjs/swagger — API documentation

## Backend — FORBIDDEN
- ❌ TypeORM, Sequelize, Drizzle, raw SQL — use Prisma only
- ❌ Express directly — use NestJS abstractions
- ❌ winston, bunyan — use nestjs-pino
- ❌ Any other metrics lib — use prom-client

## Database
- PostgreSQL 16 only
- All schema changes go through `prisma/schema.prisma`
- Run `npx prisma migrate dev` after schema changes
- Never use `$queryRaw` unless absolutely unavoidable
